	<h1 class="title">肯德基新广告拉雀巢和中粮为食品安全背书</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
